{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, how to fuse data from different modalities and train the relevant detection models to migrate to multi-modal data will be the focus of future research.",
    "(3) Video detection: There are a good deal of issues in video detection involving redundant feature information, video focus disorder, and occlusion, and so on, resulting in lower computational redundancy and detection accuracy.",
    "Therefore, the study of object detection algorithms based on video sequences will become one of the future research directions.",
    "Transformer (Vaswani et al. 2017), with its strong capabilities in long-range modeling and parallelized sequence processing, has gradually attracted the interest of researchers in the fields of image processing and computer vision.",
    "It has demonstrated excellent performance in applications such as object tracking, image generation, and image enhancement."
  ]
}